snippet.title: Shang Mu Architect - SAGE Update
snippet.description:
Hello, everyone! Shang Mu Architect has a new major update with lots of new features, just in time for SAGE 2021!



Downloads:



Our SAGE booth:

https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/shang-mu-architect.873/


Our GitHub page:

https://github.com/whitelilydragon/ShangMuArchitect/releases/tag/1.0.2.0


Read the full changelog here, it's a long one!
https://github.com/whitelilydragon/ShangMuArchitect/releases/download/1.0.2.0/Changelog.1.0.2.0.txt
